      "for_process": "lifecycle",
      "input_artifacts": ["change-start-request"],
      "output_artifacts": ["opened-unit-of-work"],
      "mechanism": "mixed",
      "mechanism_detail": "The definition of a change-start lifecycle activity: a sulis-change start completed and a unit of work was opened. LifecycleRuns that record a change being opened point their step ref here (sulis:viaStep). The per-run specificity (primitive, slug) the old free step_name string carried is carried by the run's run_id / inputs_ref fields, not by this Plan.",
