      "for_process": "lifecycle",
      "input_artifacts": ["change-ship-request"],
      "output_artifacts": ["shipped-unit-of-work"],
      "mechanism": "mixed",
      "mechanism_detail": "The definition of a change-ship lifecycle activity: a sulis-change mark-shipped completed and a unit of work landed. LifecycleRuns that record a change shipping point their step ref here (sulis:viaStep). Per-run detail is carried by the run's run_id / outputs_ref fields, not by this Plan.",
